and by extension, what made King of Dragons Pass unique.

10
00:00:39,427 --> 00:00:45,653
So some people say that the game is sort of a cross between a choose your own adventure

11
00:00:45,874 --> 00:00:51,959
and civilization, and really neither of those is true. On the other hand, I don't think

12
00:00:52,340 --> 00:00:58,346
Touch Arcade is completely wrong. It does combine narrative and a turn-based economic

13
00:00:58,386 --> 00:01:02,790
game, but it's trying to do things that neither genre alone can do.

14
