The shortest description of the games I've seen is,

15
00:01:08,415 --> 00:01:09,356
it's a strategy book.

16
00:01:09,536 --> 00:01:10,816
This is what one of the players said.

17
00:01:13,498 --> 00:01:16,440
So the game is, in fact, a combination

18
00:01:16,460 --> 00:01:17,421
