19
00:01:17,801 --> 00:01:20,983
You're guiding a small clan of the Rider people, rather than

20
00:01:21,003 --> 00:01:23,764
any one individual, or even a group of heroes.

21
00:01:24,665 --> 00:01:27,687
Your clan recently migrated because during the Gods War,

22
00:01:27,867 --> 00:01:29,908
your city got buried under a glacier.

23
00:01:31,497 --> 00:01:36,141
The core loop of the game is to take actions, which are sort of the turn-based strategy

24
00:01:36,501 --> 00:01:36,901
side.

25
00:01:37,622 --> 00:01:42,806
For example, a venture there, like expanding your fields.

26
00:01:42,826 --> 00:01:51,773
As these actions take time to do, events will occur and you respond to the events.

27
00:01:52,734 --> 00:01:57,117
So the strategy game is sort of a skeleton on which we can add stories.

28
00:01:59,206 --> 00:02:02,908
