00:13:18,984 --> 00:13:20,825
to make a bargaining roll, basically.

204
00:13:21,545 --> 00:13:23,126
And this has two possible outcomes.

205
00:13:23,166 --> 00:13:24,046
They could win or lose.

206
00:13:24,974 --> 00:13:28,775
And we also set a degree of success.

207
00:13:28,855 --> 00:13:31,436
It's by convention the variable Q, which lets us have

