00:13:31,456 --> 00:13:35,257
like really terrible failures or marginal successes.

209
00:13:35,317 --> 00:13:37,558
And I think this one here is a marginal success.

210
00:13:38,238 --> 00:13:40,479
They get a handsome price, but it's the smallest possible

211
00:13:40,539 --> 00:13:41,179
handsome price.

212
00:13:44,044 --> 00:13:48,467
So the scenes are our major building block

213
00:13:48,627 --> 00:13:49,848
of procedural content.

214
00:13:50,308 --> 00:13:52,389
There's also some other types of scripts.

215
00:13:53,009 --> 00:13:54,971
For example, news can also be interactive,

216
00:13:55,011 --> 00:13:56,211
but it's not illustrating.

