00:14:23,114 --> 00:14:24,376
can do appropriate things.

225
00:14:26,400 --> 00:14:27,902
Scenes are often consequences.

226
00:14:28,502 --> 00:14:30,744
Here we're triggering another scene three seasons

227
00:14:31,285 --> 00:14:32,085
after right now.

228
00:14:33,186 --> 00:14:37,410
And this is also one of the ways we get those longer story

